Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.54,screen,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&\b0\fs40\bord2.5\fax-0.030711\frx0.5671\fry-0.4136\xbord0.74\ybord1.03\fscx70\pos(1068.96,439.54)\frz354.8\3a&H00&}#绝对不能原谅
